IMPORTANT NOTICE FOR SAFETY-CRITICAL APPLICATIONS:

This software is designed for use in industrial control systems. While it
implements safety features aligned with IEC 61508 SIL 2 concepts, it has NOT
been formally certified to SIL 2 or any other safety integrity level.

Users of this software in safety-critical applications must:
1. Conduct their own safety analysis
2. Validate the software for their specific use case
3. Implement additional safety measures as required
4. Comply with all applicable regulations and standards

The authors assume no liability for use in safety-critical applications without
proper validation and certification.
